title: Chocolate Comfort Foods
description:
Chocolate Comfort Foods by Rita M. Harris

Overview: The chocoholics cookbook. Written by Rita Harris, the author of Simply Divine and Comfort Foods has written this book of recipes for appetizers, beverages, breakfast, brownies, cakes, candy, cheesecakes, cookies, desserts, main dishes and pies, all with different types of chocolate included. When you are ready to imbibe on a meal full of nature's own aphrodisiac, this is the book for you
